code: @Override public StreamPartitioner<Tuple> createPartitioner() {     StreamPartitioner<Tuple> partitioner = new RebalancePartitioner<>().     assertFalse(partitioner.isBroadcast()).     return partitioner. }

@Test public void testSelectChannelsInterval() {     final int numberOfChannels = 3.     streamPartitioner.setup(numberOfChannels).     int initialChannel = streamPartitioner.selectChannel(serializationDelegate).     assertTrue(0 <= initialChannel).     assertTrue(numberOfChannels > initialChannel).     for (int i = 1. i <= 3. i++) {         assertSelectedChannel((initialChannel + i) % numberOfChannels).     } }
